PlayerController: 
+ Move
+ Rotate
+ Run (Hold Right mouse button)

GrabSystem: 
- Grab object (Hold Shift-Ready to grab object (on the center of screen appears point), Release Shift (Grab Object)).
- Release object (Hold Shift-Ready to release object (in center of screen appears point), Release Shift (release object on shelf or ground))

- Placing Objects on specific area (shelf for example): placing on grid and remember what exactly area is occupied.
- Selling System
- Buying System

General tasks:
- Set price
- Grab object
- Release object
- Place object
- Sell object
- Buy object
